Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call it the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!  OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any comment, professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never know till we open it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've barely started to scratch the surface.
Comment: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:48.73,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,somebody says something????? interviewer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:03:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!  Wait!  Who are you?!  Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK, Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the dream again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been seeing it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're excavating the old grave mound in the park again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The archaeological team from R University is heading the survey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.  Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!  Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage.  Mikage.  Mikage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage, can't you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What happened to you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate if you stopped chatting with your sister telepathically during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:39.44,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're reading my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not thinking about those tadpoles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you staring at?  Don't look at me!  Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:08.29,Default,Daijoji,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, stop the nonsense and get back to the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she had her bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she was feeling good though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked dazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's home.  Thank god...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?  Tadpoles on every single page.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, what's wrong?  Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor said it's probably just a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fever hasn't gone down yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave her medicine though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?  A slate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a fireball to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure looks strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she draw, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarashina, what about the picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a "magatama".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Magatama"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An accessory the ancient people used to wear.  See?  There's a hole here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They put string through here, and used it as things like necklaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accessory?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think.  My uncle's an archaeologist.  Wanna talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm!  I think it's a picture of a "magatama."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all?  Is there anything else you can see in this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Magatama" was a very popular object for decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there's nothing much I can pick up from just this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, is this the "magatama" you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, we found that "magatama" from the grave mound on Mount Kokura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:09:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike last time 20 years ago, this time it's a full-scale excavation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage...  Mikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, answer me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're going a bit overboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:11:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about a connection between Mikage's illness and the grave mound.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how worried you're about her, but how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the woman wearing a red "magatama."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was a dream, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.  Mikage's not into history at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she'd see a dream like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gotta be some connection with the grave mound.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he was a very rich class rich man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think our man was a very happy man who spent his life in luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luxury?  Wasn't he lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're interested in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I personally often see dreams about ancient people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was an easy life in the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean in the modern day, it's boring and cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sure tough being a man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't be so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So was there no connection with the grave after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thoughts of people in the past sound romantic enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the way you always think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.  I'm not talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maa, Tomomi !
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tomomi? Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head... Mikage... Mikage's suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!  Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi !
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is that woman?  Didn't you lead a happy life?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, let's go home.  I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi... Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, a red "magatama?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't found anything like that around the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind you we haven't gone into the casket room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Casket room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is the casket room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no red magatama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, you're the man in the dream, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tell me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?  Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't ya gonna go to the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could the club president forget about the practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Tomomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't show up today, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god.  Her fever's down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that magatama.  She wanted to give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:19:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scuba diving?!  What happened to you?  The water's still darn cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you know somebody who's into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I can get you equipment, but don't tell me you've gone weird, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please?  You're the only one I can count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. OK. OK. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm all set.  Mikage, you can see where the red "magatama" is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, teleport me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two three!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me big for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, I told you where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lid was closed when I came last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Yoshimura said he was a happy man who spent his life in luxury, but that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been there with the memory of a tragedy fifteen hundred years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't be.  He's a wonderful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sad story, but I envy him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an awesome guitarist!  You cheer for him too Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Miracle Girls,\N"Whirlwind  in  Tomomi"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda, don't leave Tomomi alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:12.09,notes,note,0000,0000,0046,,{\a6}Original air date Mar 19, 1993.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.68,0:22:07.76,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:11.25,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
