Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.37,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:17.90,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:24.51,credits,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a5}Noda Yuhya...........Yamaguchi Kappei\NKurashige Hideaki...Shiozawa Kaneto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:31.51,notes,note,0000,0000,0046,,{\a6}Miracle Girls on internet http://www.tcp.com/doi/miracle/miracle.html
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:37.89,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:37.94,notes,note,0000,0000,0046,,{\a6}Miracle Girls Original Soundtrack Sony Records SRCL 2574
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:45.46,credits,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a7}Shinichiroh Kageura...Ken Yamaguchi\NDaijohji Rumiko.................Sakuma Rei
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:49.78,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:51.80,credits,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a5}Yamagishi Kouhei.......Nobuh Tobita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:57.89,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say ``I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:05.47,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:11.08,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:14.45,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:20.24,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:22.75,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:26.32,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:29.45,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:33.62,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,are better than one of us.
